# Johnny G's Restaurant - Project Context for Layout & Styling

## CRITICAL STYLING RULES

### Hybrid Styling Approach (MANDATORY)

**Vanilla CSS (CSS Variables) - USE FOR:**
- Theme colors: `var(--theme-bg-primary)`, `var(--theme-text-body)`, `var(--theme-accent)`
- Typography: `var(--font-fjalla-one)`, `var(--font-size-3xl)`, `var(--line-height-tight)`
- Any property that needs GSAP animation or theme switching

**Tailwind CSS - USE FOR:**
- Layout: `flex`, `grid`, `block`, `relative`, `absolute`
- Spacing: `p-4`, `m-6`, `gap-8`, `space-x-4`
- Sizing: `w-full`, `h-screen`, `max-w-4xl`
- Responsive: `md:flex`, `lg:grid`, `sm:text-lg`
- Borders: `border`, `rounded-lg`, `border-2`
- Shadows: `shadow-lg`, `shadow-xl`

### NEVER USE:
- ❌ Tailwind color classes for theme colors (`bg-white`, `text-black`, `dark:bg-gray-900`)
- ❌ Hardcoded colors for theme-aware elements (`#ffffff`, `#000000`)
- ❌ Tailwind typography classes for theme typography (`text-3xl`, `font-bold`)

## Component Structure Pattern

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT PATTERN
<div
  className="flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto"  // Tailwind: layout
  style={{
    backgroundColor: 'var(--theme-bg-primary)',          // Vanilla CSS: color
    color: 'var(--theme-text-body)',                    // Vanilla CSS: color
    fontFamily: 'var(--font-fjalla-one)',               // Vanilla CSS: typography
    fontSize: 'var(--font-size-2xl)'                    // Vanilla CSS: typography
  }}
>
```

## Theme Colors (CSS Variables)

**Day Theme:**
- `--theme-bg-nav: #334D2D`
- `--theme-bg-primary: #ffffff`
- `--theme-bg-secondary: #f5f5f5`
- `--theme-text-primary: #FFFFFF`
- `--theme-text-body: #171717`
- `--theme-accent: #B29738`

**Night Theme:**
- `--theme-bg-nav: #011A0C`
- `--theme-bg-primary: #011A0C`
- `--theme-bg-secondary: #022414`
- `--theme-text-primary: #FFFFFF`
- `--theme-text-body: #FFFFFF`
- `--theme-accent: #B29738`

## Typography (CSS Variables)

**Font Families:**
- `var(--font-geist-sans)` - Body text
- `var(--font-geist-mono)` - Code/monospace
- `var(--font-yellowtail)` - Decorative (use `.text-decorative` class)
- `var(--font-fjalla-one)` - Headings (h1-h6 auto-styled)

**Font Sizes:** `--font-size-xs` to `--font-size-8xl`
**Line Heights:** `--line-height-tight` to `--line-height-loose`
**Letter Spacing:** `--letter-spacing-tighter` to `--letter-spacing-widest`

## Animation-Ready Structure

**Always include:**
- `ref` attributes for GSAP targeting
- `data-animate` attributes for easy selection
- CSS variables for animatable properties
- Don't set initial `transform` or `opacity` in styles (let GSAP handle it)

```tsx
<div
  ref={containerRef}
  data-animate="container"
  className="flex flex-col gap-4"
  style={{
    backgroundColor: 'var(--theme-bg-primary)',
    color: 'var(--theme-text-body)'
  }}
>
```

## Theme Context Usage

```tsx
"use client";
import { useTheme } from "@/contexts/ThemeContext";

const { theme, toggleTheme } = useTheme();
// theme: "day" | "night"
```

## Utility Functions

```tsx
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils";

// Use for Tailwind classes only
<div className={cn("flex", condition && "md:flex-row")}>
```

## File Structure

- Components: `src/components/`
- Pages: `src/app/[page-name]/page.tsx`
- Contexts: `src/contexts/`
- Utilities: `src/lib/utils.ts`
- Data: `src/data/`

## Key Reminders

1. **Always use CSS variables** for theme colors and typography
2. **Use Tailwind** only for layout, spacing, and utilities
3. **Add transitions** for theme-aware elements: `transition-colors duration-300`
4. **Mark client components** with `"use client"` when using hooks
5. **Structure for animation** with refs and data attributes
6. **Mobile-first** responsive design with Tailwind breakpoints

## Common Patterns

**Theme-Aware Container:**
```tsx
<main 
  className="min-h-screen p-8 transition-colors duration-300"
  style={{ backgroundColor: 'var(--theme-bg-primary)' }}
>
```

**Decorative Heading:**
```tsx
<h1 
  className="text-decorative"
  style={{
    fontSize: 'var(--font-size-6xl)',
    color: 'var(--theme-accent)'
  }}
>
```

**Themed Card:**
```tsx
<div 
  className="p-6 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300"
  style={{
    backgroundColor: 'var(--theme-bg-secondary)',
    color: 'var(--theme-text-body)'
  }}
>
```

